# Rust build artifacts
/target/

# WIT dependencies, fetched into each crate by `wash build`. The WASI 0.3
# packages come from the registry; the template's own `wasmcloud:app` interface
# is resolved from the shared `wasmcloud-app/` source via each crate's wkg.toml.
# `**/` so it matches every crate's wit/deps/, not just one at the root.
**/wit/deps/

# Lock files regenerated on each fetch (the p3 WASI drafts move quickly).
**/wkg.lock

# Trash
.DS_Store
